          "html": "<section id=\"certifications\" class=\"cert-band surface-band no-reveal\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"certifications-title\">\n      <div class=\"cert-band-inner\">\n        <div class=\"cert-head\">\n          <h2 id=\"certifications-title\" class=\"section-title\">Certifications &amp; Degrees</h2>\n          <p class=\"cert-subtitle\">Credentials and formal education supporting analytics and machine learning work.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"cert-track\">\n          <a class=\"cert\" href=\"https://www.credential.net/0f4df6f1-112e-4e4e-8cb1-b97e7ecd3a3b\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n            <img src=\"img/cert_logos/purdue_global-24.png\" srcset=\"img/cert_logos/purdue_global-48.png 2x\" alt=\"Purdue University logo\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\"><span>Bachelor of Science – Data Analytics</span></a>\n          <span class=\"cert\">\n            <img src=\"img/cert_logos/eastern-24.png\" srcset=\"img/cert_logos/eastern-48.png 2x\" alt=\"Eastern University logo\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\"><span>Master of Science – Data Science</span></span>\n          <a class=\"cert\" href=\"https://www.coursera.org/account/accomplishments/specialization/certificate/CYUMPN7ZQRDA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n            <img src=\"img/cert_logos/ibm-24.png\" srcset=\"img/cert_logos/ibm-48.png 2x\" alt=\"IBM logo\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\"><span>IBM Data Analyst Certification</span></a>\n          <a class=\"cert\" href=\"https://www.coursera.org/account/accomplishments/specialization/certificate/7262X6HH5NF2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n            <img src=\"img/cert_logos/ibm-24.png\" srcset=\"img/cert_logos/ibm-48.png 2x\" alt=\"IBM logo\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\"><span>IBM Machine Learning Certification</span></a>\n          <a class=\"cert\" href=\"https://www.coursera.org/account/accomplishments/specialization/certificate/N6MNKYE4MKEP\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n            <img src=\"img/cert_logos/google-24.png\" srcset=\"img/cert_logos/google-48.png 2x\" alt=\"Google logo\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\"><span>Google Data Analytics Certification</span></a>\n          <a class=\"cert\" href=\"https://www.coursera.org/account/accomplishments/specialization/certificate/K47AGB33F8VS\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n            <img src=\"img/cert_logos/google-24.png\" srcset=\"img/cert_logos/google-48.png 2x\" alt=\"Google logo\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\"><span>Google Advanced Data Analytics Certification</span></a>\n        </div>\n        <button class=\"btn-secondary cert-modal-trigger\" type=\"button\" data-cert-modal-open>View All</button>\n      </div>\n    </section>"
